      "title": "Kanchana met Qatar\u2019s Energy Affairs State Minister",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Power and energy Minister Kanchana Wijesekara today met with Qatar\u2019s Energy Affairs State Minister and President and CEO of Qatar Energy, Saad Sherida Al-Kaabi, to discuss the supply of petroleum needs.",
        "The two ministers discussed the supply of petroleum products, liquid petrochemical gas (LPG) and Liquefied Natural Gas (LNG) to Sri Lanka to overcome the energy crisis with the assistance of Qatar Energy and the Qatar Development Fund."
      ],
